g.text: PCC Lookup - retrieve Patient Information, EHR data, diagnoses, labs, history etc
Assign patient to RT review queue
Set patient to watchlist while waiting for review
RT Reviews and determines of Patient qualifies for NIV based on current EMR, Labs and Diagnosis Codes
Add to queue to Re-Review (Reviewed) - Refused Trigger review
Order Additional Labs, including Blood Gases if Missing
Once Patient Fitted for Device move to Post Tracking
Close and initiate re-review after specified period of time.
Patient must be seen by RT Every 7 days During this time
